<pb n="0235a" id="I01.0088.0235a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="C I" n="0235a00"/><milestone n="1" unit="juan"/><head type="no">No. 88</head>
<lb ed="C I" n="0235a00"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><title>劉氏造像記</title></jhead></juan>
<lb ed="C I" n="0235a01"/><p id="pI01p0235a0101">蓋聞□<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">垂</unclear>□□□□山河□□□□□□□□□人□二□□□□□□□□□□□□□□情異庭塵
<lb ed="C I" n="0235a02"/>□<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">如</unclear>性乖<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">揚</unclear>□不足比其□。□□詎可方其識。唯有至人□□□□□□□□□迦□□□隨後供人天
<lb ed="C I" n="0235a03"/><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">悲</unclear>悼□□□□□□□□□□□狀。聖化流移。傳於東夏。其有劉氏□□<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">自</unclear>□<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">堯</unclear>□□□□扶危定傾。功
<lb ed="C I" n="0235a04"/><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">尚</unclear>九合。商周之世。□佐王□。□暨皇族。君<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">臨</unclear>万國。子孫相承二十四帝。□□□唐。難名難譬。宇宙之民。莫
<lb ed="C I" n="0235a05"/>不□□<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">今</unclear>□市迴<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">劉</unclear>□□□□等。念八倒而不返。愍九居於火宅。□法□於世界。濟三有於苦海。□遠祖
<lb ed="C I" n="0235a06"/>則趙<note n="0235001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30969;＝郡【史】</note><app n="0235001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">郡</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30969;</rdg></app>王<note n="0235002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31086;＝虎【史】</note><app n="0235002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">虎</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31086;</rdg></app>之冑胤。七世祖亮。磥硌大節。為世指南。謀若淵凝。□如江注。建<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">平</unclear>中。為趙<app source="0235001" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">郡</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30969;</rdg></app>太守。因居洨河
<lb ed="C I" n="0235a07"/>之南。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">從</unclear>祖盧。涉<note n="0235003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">獦＝獵【史】</note><app n="0235003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">獵</lem><rdg wit="【原】">獦</rdg></app>百<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">氏</unclear>。曉達方言。使歷諸國。罔不重譯。除<app source="0235002" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">虎</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31086;</rdg></app>威將軍宜春男長社令。從祖□。學博<note n="0235004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">閞＝關【史】</note><app n="0235004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">關</lem><rdg wit="【原】">閞</rdg></app>西。懷
<lb ed="C I" n="0235a08"/>邁東<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">首</unclear>。文推□橫。□藏在世。皇興二年。為殄寇將軍廣宗令。後為平遠將軍樂陵太守。從祖桀。天才自遠。
<lb ed="C I" n="0235a09"/>榮万頃之光□俶儻不群。似倉龍之渡漢。太延之初。遠使粟特。光揚天命。除伏波將軍南鄉男洛州太守。
<lb ed="C I" n="0235a10"/>從祖兄市遵。少有商角之風。長懷不世之行。嵩高惟岳。不足譬其隆崇。八<note n="0235005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31082;＝紘【史】</note><app n="0235005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">紘</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31082;</rdg></app>九野。豈得方其<note n="0235006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31087;＝寬【史】</note><app n="0235006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">寬</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31087;</rdg></app>廓。孝昌之
<lb ed="C I" n="0235a11"/>初。為盪寇將軍侍御史。天平二年。為前將軍<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">太</unclear>中大夫。從祖兄令顯。雄威自天。今古所<note n="0235007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30990;＝以【史】</note><app n="0235007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">以</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30990;</rdg></app>罕比。遒文互起。
<lb ed="C I" n="0235a12"/><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">始</unclear>終莫類其能。天平三年。除威厲將軍同蹄令。但子孫分封。荴蔬蓋世。錦衣<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">鳴</unclear>珮。光於四海。或居河託釣。
<lb ed="C I" n="0235a13"/>心慕姜公之年。或深山樂道。以崇莊老之術。遂見<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">沔</unclear>河之北。贊皇之南。山有五岳之形。水有四瀆之勢。地
<lb ed="C I" n="0235a14"/><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">帶</unclear>荊山之寶。石懷芙蓉之色。憂曇末利。四<note n="0235008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB01213;＝時【史】</note><app n="0235008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">時</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB01213;</rdg></app>吐榮。蓂莢藶英。以像晝<note n="0235009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30993;＝夜【史】</note><app n="0235009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">夜</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30993;</rdg></app>。即發育王之心。復起給孤之念。剟
<lb ed="C I" n="0235a15"/>金捨璚。迴向旡上者歟。故率宗人等。共敦斯福。其人也。皆法身大士。龍璧未變。卷翼促鱗。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">方</unclear>舒風海。敬造
<lb ed="C I" n="0235a16"/>龍華浮<note n="0235010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30744;＝圖【史】</note><app n="0235010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">圖</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30744;</rdg></app>。高門佛殿。望旋璣<app source="0235007" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">以</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30990;</rdg></app>取度。<note n="0235011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00402;＝法【史】</note><app n="0235011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">法</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00402;</rdg></app>列宿如圓<note n="0235012" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31088;＝天【史】</note><app n="0235012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">天</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31088;</rdg></app>。託兜率以垂形。藉□鷲為基則。其中復有白玉等像。
<lb ed="C I" n="0235a17"/>涌出飛來。滿月色身。旡比金聚。畫出天雲。應龍馳如相顧。刻作丹穴。神鳥翻以俱攜。乾闥撫琴。則伽<note n="0235013" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB10023;＝耶【史】</note><app n="0235013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">耶</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB10023;</rdg></app><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">廣</unclear>
<lb ed="C I" n="0235a18"/><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">不</unclear><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">自</unclear>制。緊<note n="0235014" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31083;＝那【史】</note><app n="0235014"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">那</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31083;</rdg></app>梵音。則五通耽之墜虛。蹲倚伏獸。則<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">樓</unclear>師慚其剞劂。<note n="0235015" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00370;＝虯【史】</note><app n="0235015"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">虯</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00370;</rdg></app><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">蛇</unclear>纔舉。則葉公喪其魂氣。無異千日
<lb ed="C I" n="0235a19"/>之明。豈殊雲臺之網。斯實歷代之功高。僧祇之行果。昔巨石雖廣。<note n="0235016" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31084;＝拂【史】</note><app n="0235016"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">拂</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31084;</rdg></app>輕衣如尚銷。真&CB00528;聖容。歷芥城如□
<lb ed="C I" n="0235a20"/>固。爰降短文。迺為銘曰。　　造化難測。神智旡方。廓若含虛。隱則塵藏。心水清淨。慧日舒光。四攝六度。□
<lb ed="C I" n="0235a21"/>匪津樑。獨有劉氏。世絕英倫。託志方外。遠此六塵。皮紙骨筆。八□捨身。構茲<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">靈</unclear>塔。妙相入神。<app source="0235010" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">圖</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30744;</rdg></app>廟肅肅。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">法</unclear>
<lb ed="C I" n="0235a22"/><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">堂</unclear>巍巍。琱<note n="0235017" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30645;＝金【史】</note><app n="0235017"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">金</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30645;</rdg></app>鐫<note n="0235018" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31085;＝玉【史】</note><app n="0235018"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">玉</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31085;</rdg></app>。塗以丹暉。譬彼十會。熟識是非。四生五道。莫不歸依。畫出天山。表諸神功。殊形異狀。踊
<lb ed="C I" n="0235a23"/>躍騰空。御月握日。色別玲瓏。非閉非見。誰<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">辯</unclear>西東。功踰他化。事等祇園。玉龜出灞。建立高門。猶天之固。安
<lb ed="C I" n="0235a24"/>則如練。三界雖謝。此福常存。　　維大齊武平元年歲在庚寅十一月庚戌十五日經始</p>
